flowchart LR
  MV[Metric View YAML<br/>fields, measures, materialization] --> PIPE[Managed Lakeflow pipeline]
  PIPE --> UNAGG[Unaggregated materialization<br/>semantic base snapshot]
  PIPE --> AGG1[Aggregated materialization<br/>month + region + account category]
  PIPE --> AGG2[Aggregated materialization<br/>drilldown grain]
  PIPE --> AGG3[Aggregated materialization<br/>balance grain]

  QUERY[User query<br/>SELECT ... MEASURE(...)] --> OPT[Query optimizer]
  OPT --> EXACT[Exact match]
  OPT --> ROLLUP[Rollup match]
  OPT --> FALLBACK[Unaggregated match]
  OPT --> SOURCE[Source fallback]

  EXACT --> AGG1
  ROLLUP --> AGG2
  FALLBACK --> UNAGG
  SOURCE --> MV
